      <title>拜登兜售基础设施资金以扭转北卡罗来纳州</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-02/biden-touts-infrastructure-funds-in-bid-to-flip-north-carolina</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统乔·拜登痛斥了反对他的标志性基础设施法的共和党人，该法为北卡罗来纳州的铅管拆除提供资金，因为他试图为这个战场州做出一次成功的尝试。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-02/biden-touts-infrastructure-funds-in-bid-to-flip-north-carolina</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 22:28:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>佛罗里达州共和党人就世界杯筹备工作向拜登施压</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-02/biden-pressed-on-world-cup-preparations-by-florida-republicans</link>
      <description><![CDATA[佛罗里达州共和党议员向拜登政府施压，要求其加大对迈阿密等美国城市举行的 2026 年世界杯比赛的安全和后勤准备工作的投入。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-02/biden-pressed-on-world-cup-preparations-by-florida-republicans</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 22:06:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国主要立法者希望 FTC 调查 TikTok 利用儿童进行游说的情况</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-02/us-china-committee-wants-ftc-probe-into-tiktok-s-use-of-kids-to-lobby-congress</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国众议院主要议员呼吁联邦贸易委员会调查 TikTok 官员是否违反了保护儿童的法律，并利用这款流行应用敦促未成年用户游说国会。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-02/us-china-committee-wants-ftc-probe-into-tiktok-s-use-of-kids-to-lobby-congress</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 21:41:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
