    <item>
      <title>联合国称重建加沙将在二十年内耗资 500 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-02/rebuilding-gaza-to-cost-50-billion-over-two-decades-un-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一位联合国官员周四表示，以色列与哈马斯战争后重建加沙的长期成本可能达到 500 亿美元，并且需要近二十年的时间。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-02/rebuilding-gaza-to-cost-50-billion-over-two-decades-un-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 18:40:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
